Package edu.harvard.cs262.DistributedGame.VotingGame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VotingClient
    The VotingClient class contains the code that the clients run in the Voting Game.
    VotingClusterServer
    The VotingClusterServer class contains the code that the servers run in the Voting Game.
    VotingCommand
    The VotingCommand class represents a command in the Voting Game.
    VotingCommandProcessor
    The VotingCommandProcessor class processes the commands the clients send and chooses the ones to execute.
    VotingDisplay
    The VotingDisplay class is the display that the clients see when they play the Voting Game.
    VotingGame
    The VotingGame class represents and instance of the voting game.
    VotingGameTest  
    VotingInputParser
    The VotingInputParser class parses the input given from the clients into VotingCommand objects
    VotingState
    The VotingState class represents the current state of the game, which consists of the value of the game and the frame number associated with that value.
